{"tid":2456320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓正稱中國開放的大門只會愈開愈大","createTime":"2021-03-21T23:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T02:22:33.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7375a99840176df26c5786995980ea9d509f4b8d","tid":2456320,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T23:26:58.000Z","msg":"韓正稱中國開放的大門只會愈開愈大<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%9F%93%E6%AD%A3%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%80%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%83%E6%84%88%E9%96%8B%E6%84%88%E5%A4%A7-133519912.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2584%2588%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2584%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7-133519912.html&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=9801e6b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%9F%93%E6%AD%A3%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%80%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%83%E6%84%88%E9%96%8B%E6%84%88%E5%A4%A7-133519912.html</a><br />\n<br />\n國務院副總理韓正在北京出席中國發展高層論壇時表示,中國開放的大門不會關閉,只會愈開愈大,受疫情衝擊影響,世界經濟復甦基礎仍不穩,中國願與世界加強協調,實施有利的財政及金融政策,維護全球產業鏈、供應鏈的穩定,推動世界經濟早日走出危機的陰影,繼續推進高質量「一帶一路」,深化與沿線國家的合作。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">韓正表示,中國14億人口中,有4億人為中等收入,形成超大規模的市場,中國經濟今年延續穩定恢復的態勢,歡迎各國企業分享中國開放的大市場和發展機遇,亦將調整優化進口稅稅收政策,進一步縮減外資准入負面清單等。 <br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n韓正稱,國內生產總值由5年前不到70萬億元人民幣,增加至去年超過100萬億元人民幣,人均國內生產總值突破1萬美元,改革開放實現重要突破。"},{"pid":"b3ef086f3b3371e6ab944fa811fde0b1bbf93385","tid":2456320,"uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T23:30:06.000Z","msg":"中共慢慢玩內循環啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2020/1015/20201015024429760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2020%2F1015%2F20201015024429760.jpg&h=9180abf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2700000/2703256/0722_XI_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2700000%2F2703256%2F0722_XI_1024.jpg&h=f1505408&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9a906953fc5accc5418088daa21ae2ef19a0c2e","tid":2456320,"uid":36901,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T23:31:50.000Z","msg":"on9仔<br />\n而家全世界釘緊木板封撚左你個門口呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7434c0edc716521cc01588bd0e0c4c76708124fb","tid":2456320,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89481d522b2527987da4ebac65ce3d5cd9a7f0f5","tid":2456320,"uid":9542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"越戰狼，你個閪就真係越開越大"},{"pid":"91931d9cde5f8fc9cfb45579a7f47a075d5143ff","tid":2456320,"uid":84044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:42:25.000Z","msg":"閪門咋？"},{"pid":"8b72fbdc7c6e11e07a86a32cc68f200bc9cb3f0a","tid":2456320,"uid":227271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:46:39.000Z","msg":"D臭味攻晒出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無人黎架啦臭到咁，快D封柒埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1849aef1d0f625a482e32d03f4d0f0e1bc789b","tid":2456320,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:50:32.000Z","msg":"LeBron James如果唔跟Nike解約, 就係辱華, 要俾中國人民封殺!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2460269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2460269</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<